name: Taiwan Ichiban

reviews.text:
Nice place to dine in. Clean and spacious.
Opted to try this. Kinda very similar to Supreme pork chop rice. I chose the honey  glazed chicken chop rice. Rather nice crisp outside. Meat is still tender and moist. Rice portion could be more as it seems too little to go with a larger piece of meat. Overall it alright.
The space is freshly built and very clean. You can eat rouleau rice. There seems to be a further discount for nearby students. The quantity is quite large and the satisfaction is highüëç
